Package: taudac-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dkms (>= 2.1.0.0)
Recommends: linux-headers-generic | linux-headers | raspberrypi-kernel-headers
Description: DKMS source for TauDAC ASoC driver
 This package provides the TauDAC driver in a form suitable for use with DKMS.
 .
 The TauDAC driver provides ALSA System on Chip (ASoC) support for the TauDAC,
 a high-quality audio DAC for Raspberry Pi. It includes:
  * snd-soc-taudac: Main TauDAC machine driver
  * snd-soc-wm8741: WM8741 codec driver
  * clk-si5351: Si5351 clock generator driver
 .
 The kernel module will be automatically built for the currently running kernel
 and automatically rebuilt for any new kernel installations.
